{
  "id": "adv_bond_mhk_01_04",
  "title": "miho4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……今日も散々だったわ\n久々に会ったプロデューサーには皮肉を言われるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… today was a disaster again\nI heard a sarcastic comment from a producer I hadn't seen in a long time",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 5.4066288527
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "franはロケ弁のおかずが少ないって文句を言うし\nkanaは、自分の分を分けてやろうとするし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran complained that there weren't enough side dishes in the location lunch box\nkana‚ tried to share her share…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 15.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "それは、いい話に聞こえるんだけど\nでも、きっとそうではないのよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That‚ sounds like a good story\nBut‚ surely it's not…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.4666678111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "「kana優しいから貧乏な山田さんにお弁当あげる」\nなんて煽り散らかして、楽屋に割り箸が舞わなければね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'kana is kind‚ so share my lunch box with poor Yamada-san'\nShe was so provocative‚ disposable chopsticks were flying all over the dressing room",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 31.7666678111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ま……まぁ、今日も大変だったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W… Well‚ you had a hard day today",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.7666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 36.7333344777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんがなんだか凄い恐い顔をしてたから\n愚痴が溜まってるんだろうと思ったけど、案の定だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "miho-san had a really scary face‚\nso I thought she was frustrated‚ just as I expected",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7333344777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 45.8000011444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "……その挙げ句\nfranとkanaの意見はぴたりと一致するし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No matter what‚\nfran and kana's opinions were in perfect agreement",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 50.7333344777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "それも、いいことって訳じゃないのね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That‚ wouldn't be a good thing either…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7333344777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 55.1000011444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "……あの二人が結託するなんていうのは\n私をおちょくって、馬鹿にする時だけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Those two only collude\nwhen they mock me and treat me like a fool",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1000011444,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hit-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5866.666666700005
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hit-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9933.3333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.5666678111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "敵の敵は味方！！\n戦場のセオリーを楽屋で実行せんでもよろしい！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The enemy of my enemy is my friend!!\nThere's no need to apply battlefield theory in the dressing room!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.3333344777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "人が健康のために弁当に入れていたぬか漬けを、声を\n揃えて、若さが感じられないと馬鹿にしおってからに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They all say that nukazuke‚ which people put in their lunch boxes for health‚\ndoesn't make them feel young‚ and they treat them like fools!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3333344777,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hit-02.m4a",
          "delay": 15599.998855599992
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "今度、居眠りしている間に、鼻にねじ込んでやろうか！\n乳酸菌の効能も知らぬ愚か者どもが！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next time‚ while they're sleeping‚ I'll shove some up their noses!\nThose idiots who don't even know the benefits of probiotics!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.8000011444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "肌の手入れのついでに\n脳味噌まですべすべにしおって、情けない！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While you're taking care of your skin‚\nyou've also washed away your brain cells‚ how pathetic!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.3666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 88.5666678111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "いつもとは違うバーに来て正解だったわ\n人目がある所では、これはインパクトあるわよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was right to come to a different bar than usual\nThis definitely makes an impact‚ in public…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.9000011444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、この口調……mihoさん、こう見えて\nミリタリーものが好きなのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ that tone of voice… miho-san‚ even though you look like this\ndo you like military stuff?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.9000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 106.0000011444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "ミリタリーもの？　別に好きじゃないわよ\n話題作をいくつか観たことはあるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Military stuff? Not really\nI've seen a few popular ones‚ though",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 112.9666678111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "……そ、そう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I-I see",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.9666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.5000011444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "はっ。貴様、なぜ私のことを聞き出そうとする！？\nもしやkana達のスパイではあるまいな！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ You‚ why are you trying to find out about me!?\nAre you sure you're not a spy for kana and the others!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.5000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.7666678111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私はただ、mihoさんが疲れてそうだから\n飲みに誘っただけで……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I just invited you out for a drink\nbecause you looked so tired…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.7666678111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 131.4333344777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "やかましい！　さあ、まず貴様の所属と名を吐け！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Quiet! Come on‚ tell me your name and affiliation!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4333344777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 137.2000011444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_04-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "えええ……ほ、星見プロダクション所属\nサニーピースの佐伯遙子です～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eheheh… I-I'm a member of Hoshimi Prods‚\nHaruko Saeki from Sunny Peace~!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.2000011444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bar-00-night",
      "startTime": 141.9000011444
    }
  ]
}